@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="privacy-page" style="max-width: 720px;">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 2026</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you register for Advanced Chat, we collect your email address and a securely hashed password. We also store chat messages and room membership data necessary for the operation of the service.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>To provide and maintain the chat service</li>
        <li>To authenticate your identity and authorize access to rooms</li>
        <li>To display your messages and profile information to other room members</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>Your data is stored locally in a SQLite database. We do not share your personal information with third parties. Chat messages are retained as long as the chat room exists.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request deletion of your account and associated data at any time by contacting the administrator.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this policy, please contact the site administrator.</p>
</div>
